=Lead data from previous node:

Company name: {{ $json.company_name || "Unknown Company" }}

City: {{ $json.city || "" }}

State: {{ $json.state || "" }}

Country: {{ $json.country || "" }}

Website: {{ $json.website || "" }}

LinkedIn URL: {{ $json.linkedin_url || "" }}

Source: {{ $json.source || "" }}

Based on this data and your general knowledge, write:

COMPANY OVERVIEW

2–3 bullet points describing what this company most likely does, who it serves, and roughly how it operates (local vs broader, B2B vs B2C, etc.).

POSSIBLE COMPETITORS

2–4 bullet points describing the kinds of competitors it probably has and how those competitors typically present themselves online.

TYPICAL WEBSITE PATTERNS

3–5 bullet points describing typical website / landing page patterns for companies like this (sections, messaging, CTAs, trust elements).

LANDING PAGE RECOMMENDATIONS

3–5 bullet points with concrete suggestions for what a new or improved landing page for this company should emphasize.

If the company name and data make the niche obvious, you may talk specifically about that niche. If it’s unclear, keep the description slightly more general but still practical.

